WEBVTT

00:05.480 --> 00:06.240
Archers

00:06.800 --> 00:07.920
Follow my orders

00:10.880 --> 00:11.480
Fire arrows

00:17.040 --> 00:17.800
Fire arrows

00:22.880 --> 00:24.000
No!

00:30.080 --> 00:30.600
Faster

00:30.680 --> 00:31.240
Move forward

00:32.720 --> 00:35.000
Faster, no retreat, retreat and die

00:39.120 --> 00:40.720
Archers, ready

00:47.600 --> 00:50.280
The northern expedition may one day succeed

00:50.600 --> 00:53.120
But they will never see it

00:53.680 --> 00:55.280
The stench of blood rises beneath the walls

00:55.520 --> 00:57.040
You feel your throat tighten

00:57.200 --> 00:58.200
Your stomach churns

00:58.480 --> 01:00.600
But you remain standing on the city walls

01:01.160 --> 01:01.720
You know

01:02.200 --> 01:03.120
For the rest of your life

01:03.400 --> 01:05.320
You will never forget this day

01:06.080 --> 01:07.920
When we finally defeat the Wuzhao

01:08.240 --> 01:10.200
You will repay them a hundredfold

01:11.560 --> 01:12.320
Fire arrows

01:47.400 --> 01:49.000
Fire arrows
